data.description: Assumeable Loan- under 2.5%.   AMAZING townhouse ! 3 large bedrooms and 2 large bathrooms upstairs; 1/2 bath on main floor. ! Attached 1 car garage. Over 1600 sf of air conditioned living space. Lakewood Village is a gated community. Large eat-in kitchen with pantry. Enjoy your view from  Living room and large screened lanai of the wooded preserve. Unit has Hurricane shutters . Community has Pool & Hot Tub.    This community has a community pool, has roof, lawn maintenance, cable and flood insurance included in HOA.
